---
title: Creamy Caper-Dill Salmon "En Papillote"  with Buttery Wild Rice Pilaf and Broccolini
description: Fish cooked "en papillote" is like a present, a wonderful individual parcel to open, full of the aromas of fish, herbs, lemon and veggies. Simple and healthful, this is a new technique that is bound to be a favourite!

